===股道===
[[File:Railway_map_around_New_York_City_MkII.svg|thumb]]
大中央總站拥有28个（44個月台编号）和67個[[股道|股道]]（43条使用中），为[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]最多车站股道记录的拥有者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/largest-railway-station-(no-of-platforms)|title=Largest railway station (no. of platforms)|website=Guinness World Records|access-date=December 11, 2018|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304083103/https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/largest-railway-station-(no-of-platforms)|dead-url=no}}</ref>。所有股道均为[[大都会北方铁路|大都会北方铁路]]使用。在车站建成初期设有123条股道，这个数字包括公用股道和存车线<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.interestingamerica.com/2010-12-08_Grand_Central_Terminal_by_Grigonis.html|title=Unknown Grand Central Terminal, New York City, New York|work=Interesting America|access-date=2021-08-13|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801063327/http://www.interestingamerica.com/2010-12-08_Grand_Central_Terminal_by_Grigonis.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="RN p. 136" />。站台股道建于向北下坡的路基上，以方便进站时能更快减速、出站时能更快加速<ref name="Fitch Waite p. 4" />。

上层月台设有42条股道，其中29条办理客运业务，自东向西编号11-42，不设12、22、31道<ref>{{cite web|title=Metro-North Railroad Track Charts, Maintenance Program, Interlocking Diagrams, & Yard Diagrams|publisher=Metro-North Railroad|page=84|url=https://assets.documentcloud.org/documents/2647944/Operations-Metro-North-Railroad-Track-Charts.pdf|date=2015|access-date=May 12, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108132506/https://assets.documentcloud.org/documents/2647944/Operations-Metro-North-Railroad-Track-Charts.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。上层旅客月台东侧为东存车场，设有编号1-10的存车线共10条；西侧设有西存车场，编号38-42；两个存车场间设有[[灯泡线|灯泡线]]连接<ref name="RN p. 138" /><ref name=":42"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gricer.com/gct/1-line-a.pdf|title=Grand Central Terminal, Upper Level|date=2004|first=Peter R.|last=Samson|access-date=2021-08-13|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417084350/http://www.gricer.com/gct/1-line-a.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Fitch Waite p. 5" />。东存车场北侧为Lex车场，位于[[紐約華爾道夫酒店|紐約華爾道夫酒店]]下方，所在处曾经为中央车站的发电厂。该车场设有12条股道（51-65道，无57、58、62道）、2个华尔道夫酒店私人乘降月台（{{link-en|61道 (纽约市)|Track 61 (New York City)|61、63道}}），目前已不再使用<ref name=":42"/><ref name="RN p. 150" /><ref>{{harvnb|ps=.|Belle|Leighton|2000|p=67}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.columbia.edu/~brennan/abandoned/gct61.html|title=Grand Central Terminal, Waldorf-Astoria platform|access-date=November 18, 2009|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106232528/http://www.columbia.edu/~brennan/abandoned/gct61.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7830369.stm|title=The secret below Grand Central Station|date=January 16, 2009|access-date=January 17, 2009|work=BBC News|archive-date=2021-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210813054154/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7830369.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.columbia.edu/~brennan/abandoned/gct61.html|title=Grand Central Terminal, Waldorf-Astoria platform|author=Joseph Brennan|date=2002|access-date=May 2, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106232528/http://www.columbia.edu/~brennan/abandoned/gct61.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2014/05/01/fdr_secret_subway_in_the_amazing_spider_man_2_the_hidden_train_station_used.html|title=Is the Secret Subway in the New Spider-Man Real? Explained.|author=Forrest Wickman|date=May 1, 2014|magazine=Slate|access-date=2021-08-13|archive-date=2020-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200216121850/http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2014/05/01/fdr_secret_subway_in_the_amazing_spider_man_2_the_hidden_train_station_used.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

车站下层月台设有27条股道，自东向西编号100-126<ref name=":42"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gricer.com/gct/1-line-b.pdf|title=Grand Central Terminal, Lower Level|date=2004|first=Peter R.|last=Samson|access-date=2021-08-13|archive-date=2016-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207004341/http://www.gricer.com/gct/1-line-b.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括2条现在很少使用的邮政股道和包括股道<ref name="Schlichting pp. 62-63" /><ref name="nyt19041224" />。目前仅有102-112道和114-115道使用，116-125道为建设[[长岛铁路|长岛铁路]]{{link-en|东区通道|East Side Access}}延伸站体而被拆除<ref>{{cite book|url=http://web.mta.info/capital/esa_docs/eafiles06/01%20Purpose%20and%20Need.pdf|chapter=Chapter 1: Purpose and Need|title=Environmental Impact Statement|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|date=2006|access-date=December 12, 2019|at=PDF p. 3|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304001445/http://web.mta.info/capital/esa_docs/eafiles06/01%20Purpose%20and%20Need.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
